            <description><![CDATA[
                            <h2>New Features</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Adds alternate Dock icons and an Appearance settings tab</li>
                                <li>Adds options to burn completed items on quit and/or at the end of the day</li>
                                <li>Adds donation links in the Help menu and in Settings</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2>Fixes and Improvements</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>The app now quits after the last window is closed</li>
                                <li>Includes minor interface improvements</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2>Known Issues</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>When the list is not scrolled to the top, the burning animation may appear incorrectly</li>
                            </ul>
							]]></description>
